message.entry: One or more ties for n-th place occurred when selecting objects. Some objects were not selected.
RANGE must be a two element vector [min max] or a scalar number of regions to keep.
N must be a scalar to specify 'largest' or 'smallest'.
Connected component structure must be for a 2-D image
Connectivity argument is not supported when the first input argument is a connected component structure
Input image and marker image must be the same size
